::KitKat::

She looked up from the console and at Drillbit.  She smiled at 
Drillbit. "No, we were just talking about the spark.  So far it is 
telling me very little.  The only thing that I've found out so far 
was that somewhere in the cloning prosess, the DNA was minus the gean 
for the proper skin pigment. But other than that, I haven't learned 
much." she looked at the floor and sighed.  She was exhausted, but 
the was trying to not let it show.
